# ALPE Games — catalog scope

- Do not add backend APIs, auth, databases, or user accounts unless explicitly requested.
- Registry-driven pages only: game metadata lives in `data/games.registry.json`.
- Keep embed hosting engine-agnostic (`iframe`, `external`, `self`).
- Do not embed secrets in the catalog repo.
- Prefer small, focused PRs; avoid redesigning the whole site during a game cycle.
